<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hé yī shì fù shén de xīn yì 迦南862</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yòng wǒ men de yǎn lèi, yòng wǒ men de qí dǎo, huàn xǐng qīn ài de tóng bāo. zài zhǔ lǐ hé ér wèi yī.
 yīn wèi wǒ men wǎng yé lù sā lěng, lù tú shàng wǒ zhēn xū yào nǐ. fēng zhōng qiān shǒu yǔ zhōng xiāng yī. wǒ
 zhēn chéng de duì nǐ shuō, wǒ zhēn de xū yào nǐ. lù tú yáo yuǎn bù néng méi yǒu nǐ. wǒ
 zhēn de xū yào nǐ. wǒ zhēn de xū yào nǐ. hé yī xiāng ài cái néng shèng guò chóu dí.
 níng shì níng tīng dà de shàng chuán lái de xiāo xī. tiān xià de hé liú tóng wǎng yī chù qù, fēng
 yǔ zhōng wǒ men qiān zhe shǒu, zhè cái shì hǎo xiōng dì. hé yī xiāng ài shě yǐ, shì fù qīn de xīn yì.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>862</hymn_number>
</song>